TASK 3 – Container Monitoring

Created monitoring directory:
sudo mkdir -p /opt/container-monitor/logs

Created monitoring script:
sudo nano /opt/container-monitor/monitor.sh

Added script content to capture:
- Timestamp
- CPU usage
- Memory usage

Made script executable:
sudo chmod +x /opt/container-monitor/monitor.sh

Configured cron job:
crontab -e

Added:
* * * * * /opt/container-monitor/monitor.sh

Verified cron service:
sudo systemctl status cron

Verified log file:
cat /opt/container-monitor/logs/monitor.log

Result:
Container CPU and memory usage logged automatically every minute.
